entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You found an remote Imperial scientific or prison outpost. Cale has advised you to not look into it any further.
entries.journal_entry_description: Investigate a new location on Dathomir
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Travel to the location on Dathomir and investigate what is going on there.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: An Imperial Outpost?  It looks like some sort of Science and Prison Labor project or something. I don't like the looks of it.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: Meet me back at my home at Mos Taike.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find Cale at his place on Mos Taike, Tatooine.
